Khartoum &mdash; The Council of Ministers chaired by the First Vice - President and National Prime Minister, Lt. Gen. Bakri Hassan Sali, heard Thursday a report on the phenomenon on watery diarrhea presented by the Federal Minister of Health, Bahr Idris Abu-Garda.The minister said the current situation shows a daily decrease in the disease cases in all the states following the wide interventions carried out by the Ministry of Health.Abu-Garda expected the full control over the disease during the coming few days.